mary_tag w-inline-block\"><div>Employment &amp; HR</div></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_image-wrapper\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"0.05\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b44ab164a8844c96471e18/6a1ef92de8f46a5863584f67_694a80dfbabc4a6edcb7c2f7_Moonstone-JMA-PHOTOGRAPHY-DSC_3645%2520-low-res.jpeg\" class=\"team-profile-large_portfolio-header_image\"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"team-header_background-icon-wrapper-copy\"><img data-scroll=\"\" data-scroll-speed=\"-0.25\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68b448d2e0ae8eda7aa370e3/6924418b395e9ab3d12cfac8_shape-2.svg\" loading=\"eager\" class=\"team-header_background-icon-copy\"></div><div data-hidden=\"live\" class=\"dark_background\"></div></header><header class=\"section_team-profile-large_header-1\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid team-profile-large_header-1_content\"><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-left\"><h2>Committed to delivering the best outcome for you</h2></div><div class=\"team-profile-large_header-1_content-right\"><div class=\"w-richtext\"><p>Anna Schiavetta is a Senior Associate Solicitor in our Employment team. Since joining in June 2022, she’s advised employer clients on a broad range of employment matters, including contracts, policies, grievances, disciplinaries, redundancies and TUPE. Her work also covers settlement agreements and the employment aspects of corporate deals.</p><p> </p><p>With strong experience in Employment Tribunal litigation, Anna regularly acts for large employers, including a major national retailer, defending claims across a range of issues.</p><p>‍</p><p>She’s part of our Holiday &amp; Home Parks team, offering specialist HR and employment advice to park owners, and delivers training on equality, diversity and workplace harassment.</p><p> </p><p>Alongside her client work, Anna volunteers at the University of Law’s pro bono clinic, providing free employment law advice and mentoring students.</p><p> </p><p>Before joining us, she completed a First Class LawDegree and Master’s at Northumbria University. She trained at a commercial firm in the North East and worked in-house for a national technology company before qualifying into private practice in Kampala.</p><p>‍</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></header><section class=\"section_expertise-video w-condition-invisible\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"wrapper_wide-screen is-light\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"expertise-video_component\"><div class=\"w-layout-grid expertise-video_content\"><div class=\"expertise-video_content-left\"><h2 class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></h2><p class=\"w-dyn-bind-empty\"></p></div><div class=\"expertise-video_content-right\"><div class=\"expertise-image_wrapper\"><img src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/plugins/Basic/assets/placeholder.60f9b1840c.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"image w-dyn-bind-empty\"></div><a href=\"/anna-schiavetta#\" class=\"expertise-video_lightbox w-inline-block w-dyn-bind-empty w-lightbox\"><img src=\"anna-schiavetta.html\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" class=\"expertise-video_lightbox-image w-dyn-bind-empty\"><div class=\"lightbox-play-icon\"><div class=\"icon-embed-large w-embed\"><svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" viewBox=\"0 0 64 64\" fill=\"none\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" clip-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M5.33301 32C5.33301 17.2724 17.2721 5.33334 31.9997 5.33334C39.0721 5.33334 45.8549 8.14286 50.8559 13.1438C55.8568 18.1448 58.6663 24.9276 58.6663 32C58.6663 46.7276 46.7273 58.6667 31.9997 58.6667C17.2721 58.6667 5.33301 46.7276 5.33301 32ZM27.1198 43.4134L42.6664 33.7067C43.2482 33.3341 43.6001 32.6909 43.6001 32C43.6001 31.3092 43.2482 30.6659 42.6664 30.2934L27.0664 20.5867C26.452 20.1993 25.6758 20.1755 25.0388 20.5244C24.4018 20.8734 24.004 21.5403 23.9998 22.2667V41.7334C23.9912 42.4774 24.3963 43.1647 25.0514 43.5174C25.7065 43.8702 26.5033 43.8301 27.1198 43.4134Z\" fill=\"CurrentColor\"></path>\n</svg></div></div><div class=\"lightbox_overlay\"></div><script type=\"application/json\" class=\"w-json\">{\n  \"items\": [],\n  \"group\": \"\"\n}</script></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></section><div class=\"section_testimonial\"><div class=\"w-embed\"><style>\n.section_testimonial:has(.w-dyn-empty) {\n  display: none;\n}\n</style></div><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"divider-horizontal\"></div><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div fs-slider-type=\"cms\" fs-slider-instance=\"fs-1-card-slider\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_instance\"><div class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation-wrapper\"><div class=\"testimonial_icon-wrapper\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/assets/69010fb7542aa2ee07e42406_quote-2.svg\" alt=\"\" class=\"testimonial_icon\"></div><div fs-slider-element=\"navigation\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_navigation\"><button fs-slider-element=\"previous\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M14.71 15.88L10.83 12l3.88-3.88a.996.996 0 1 0-1.41-1.41L8.71 11.3a.996.996 0 0 0 0 1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39 1.02.39 1.41 0c.38-.39.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button><button fs-slider-element=\"next\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_button\"><div class=\"icon-embed-small w-embed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\" class=\"iconify iconify--ic\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M9.29 15.88L13.17 12L9.29 8.12a.996.996 0 1 1 1.41-1.41l4.59 4.59c.39.39.39 1.02 0 1.41L10.7 17.3a.996.996 0 0 1-1.41 0c-.38-.39-.39-1.03 0-1.42\"></path></svg></div></button></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"list-wrapper\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div fs-slider-element=\"list\" role=\"list\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_list w-dyn-items\"><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone helped us think beyond the sessions by supporting us to consider how the legislative changes translate into day to day behaviours and what this means for our culture in anticipation for our policy to be launched. This has supported follow on training delivery internally surrounding misogyny, misogynoir and trans-misogyny. </div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Training Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">We had an excellent experience working with Moonstone. From the moment we reached out to request training, they responded quickly and took the time to meet with us early on to understand our needs and the wider organisational context. They were patient and flexible as we worked through our planning.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Training Client </div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">The team at Moonstone have given us legal advice on a number of occasions. Each team member we’ve dealt with has been very professional, efficient and helpful.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Holiday &amp; Home Parks Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Well-known, well-run and professional, the team at Moonstone cover all the core practice areas with a family feel whilst offering an air of corporate glamour. There isn&#x27;t another firm in Kampala like it.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">What makes this practice unique is their exceptional commitment to personalised service and their understanding of the specific challenges faced by clients from diverse backgrounds.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Potential clients would appreciate this firm&#x27;s strengths in employment law, their empathetic approach, and their proactive communication style. They truly stand out compared to other firms due to their collaborative team dynamic, which brings together diverse perspectives to deliver well-rounded legal solutions.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Getting legal advice was a big step for me in a difficult situation, Moonstone’ practice stands out for its client-focused approach, deep industry expertise, and commitment to putting the client first. They used a good mix cutting-edge legal strategies with a strong emphasis on technology, efficiency, and collaboration to deliver superior result and I felt ass</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Employment Client</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">Moonstone meld extremely good knowledge of employment law with excellent client care skills.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal 500</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">What stands out most is the strong sense of togetherness and feeling valued. Combined with outstanding progression opportunities, makes it an ideal place to build a career.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal500</div></div></div></div><div fs-slider-element=\"slide\" role=\"listitem\" class=\"fs-1-card-slider_slide w-dyn-item\"><div class=\"heading-style-h6\">Trusted by organisations, families and professionals across the Uganda</div><div class=\"heading-style-h4\">I was dealt with sensitively and I felt like I was given the opportunity to be heard. There is a real human touch element to the service provided.</div><div class=\"testimonial_attribute\"><div class=\"testimonial_personal-details\"><div class=\"text-weight-semibold\">Legal 500</div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><section id=\"section_blog\" element-reveal=\"trigger\" class=\"section_listing-row\"><div class=\"padding-global\"><div class=\"container-large\"><div class=\"padding-section-large\"><div class=\"listing-row_component\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-large\"><div class=\"row_heading-wrapper\"><div class=\"row_heading\"><div class=\"max-width-large\"><h2 class=\"heading-style-h2\">Read latest insights</h2><p class=\"text-size-medium\">Discover articles written by this team member</p></div></div><div class=\"button-group is-right hide-mobile-landscape\"><a href=\"/insight-hub/blog\" class=\"button is-secondary w-button\">View all blog posts</a></div></div></div><div class=\"listing_list-wrapper w-dyn-list\"><div role=\"list\" class=\"listing_list w-dyn-items\"><div role=\"listitem\" class=\"listing_item w-dyn-item\"><div hover-zoom=\"trigger\" class=\"listing_item\"><a href=\"/insight-hub/blog/strengthening-the-taw-on-tipping-the-revised-code-of-practice\" class=\"blog_item-link w-inline-block\"><div class=\"margin-bottom margin-small\"><div class=\"article_image-wrapper\"><img hover-zoom=\"target\" loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.prod.website-files.com/68